    "username":"camelm",
    "password":"siva"
}

POST - http://localhost:8080/auth/validate  [validate user]
                   (or)
       http://localhost:9876/auth/validate            
(in authrization)
bearer-token -> Token-<token-paste>
  
GET - http://localhost:9876/user/viewuser  [list users]

DELETE - http://localhost:9876/user/{id} [delete users]


